Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:47.87,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}那个时候的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.06,0:01:51.63,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}戴着无法飞翔的螺旋桨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.17,0:01:55.59,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}抬头仰望着半分天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:59.09,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}一路赤脚追逐着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:03.47,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}始终如此的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:06.60,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}也许一直在误解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.89,0:02:09.94,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}持有自信迎面生活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:20.15,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}重要的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.49,0:02:23.28,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}为了能够永久珍藏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.57,0:02:32.17,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}这份心情  一定会消失不见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:35.34,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}旋转起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:38.13,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}持有着这魔法之仗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:41.26,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}眼泪与Sunny day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:43.72,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)\blur3}溶于心中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:47.81,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}寂寞的人的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:50.35,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}会有梦想绽放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:53.06,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}不管何时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.60,0:02:56.32,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}伴随左右
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:03:00.82,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}我们一起
