Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.94,0:22:47.82,EDJ,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3a&H80\3c&H387FF8&\blur3\fad(200,200)}過ごした毎日が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.23,0:22:54.78,EDJ,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3a&H80\3c&H387FF8&\blur3\fad(200,200)}消えないでと願った
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.16,0:22:59.58,EDJ,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3a&H80\3c&H387FF8&\blur3\fad(200,200)}忘れないよ　時が過ぎ
